Paper: hep-th/9509082

Date: 1995-09-14

Title: Relativistic SUSY QM as Deformed SUSY QM

Authors: M.Arik, T.Rador (Bosphorous University), R.M.Mir-Kasimov (JINR, Dubna)

Comments: plain latex, 7 pages

The relativistic finite-difference SUSY Quantum Mechanics (QM) is developed.We show that it is connected in a natural way with the q-deformed SUSY QuantumMechanics. Simple examples are given.